           : Bruce K. 
                Anderson



                    Bruce K. Anderson

                    General Partner






Mr. Anderson co-founded WCAS and focuses on technology
investments. Prior to co-founding WCAS, Mr. Anderson spent nine
years at Automatic Data Processing (ADP). At the time of his
departure, he was Executive Vice President, President of ADP
International and a member of the Board of Directors. Before
joining ADP, Mr. Anderson spent four years in consulting. He
graduated from the University of Minnesota in 1962.




