Insider Activity


Individual




Bruce K. Anderson



Mr. Bruce K. Anderson is Independent Director at Alliance Data Systems Corp. and Co-Founder & General Partner at Welsh, Carson, Anderson & Stowe. He is on the Board of Directors at Headstrong Corp. 
Mr. Anderson was previously employed as Independent Director by Amdocs Ltd. and Director, International President & EVP by Automatic Data Processing, Inc. 
Mr. Anderson received his undergraduate degree from the University of Minnesota in1962.



